Good afternoon, can you please tell me why my company is not launching? Why my announcements do not pass the check?

Good afternoon! I'm sorry to hear that you're having trouble with your company's launch and announcements. Could you please provide more details about the platform or service you're using for your company launch and announcements? This will help me assist you better.
It's a chain of spas across the country. Here is a link to one of the sites of this service in the city of San Francisco - https://tantrik-sf.com/

Thank you for providing the link. To better assist you, could you please let me know which platform or service you're using to launch your company and make announcements? For example, are you using News Break or another service?

Got it, you're using News Break. There could be several reasons why your announcements are not passing the check. It might be due to content guidelines or technical issues. I recommend checking out our API Integration Guide for detailed instructions on how to properly set up and launch your announcements: [API Integration Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/27680147056397-API-Integration-Guide). If you continue to face issues, please contact our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance.
